###############################################
PrettyPhoto
Pre 0.1 proof of concept
###############################################

Developer
-----------------------------------------------
Nicolaas Francken [at] sunnysideup.co.nz

Requirements
-----------------------------------------------
SilverStripe 2.3.0 or greater.

Documentation
-----------------------------------------------
adds the photoviewer - pretty photo
(jQuery extension) to the site


Installation Instructions
-----------------------------------------------
add module as per usual
use PrettyPhoto::include_code()
OR
PrettyPhoto::block() to
add and remove code

any link like this:
<a href="mylargepicture.gif" rel="prettyPhoto"><img src="mysmallpicture.gif" /></a>
will automatically have a fancy pop-up link.
